      "text": [
        " مَا اسْتَشْفَى مَرِيضٌ بِمِثْلِ الْعَسَلِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ali Bin Hassan, from Musa Bin Bakr, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al Hassan<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘A patient cannot be healed like (he can) with the likes of honey’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Ali ibn Hassan from Musa ibn Bakr who has said the following: “A patient does not receive a cure as he can with honey.’” "
        ]
      }
